headline: Visa’s Global Product Drop Set for April 30th
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, April 17, 2025--Visa today announced its Product Drop event is scheduled for April 30 in San Francisco. At the event, Visa CEO Ryan McInerney and Visa Chief Product and Strategy Officer Jack Forestell will take the stage to unveil new products, solutions and technology partners that are poised to transform the next generation of commerce.
